  stimulus_text = 'The most common type of punctuation in English writing, the comma, is frequently used to separate items in a series.  But when a series contains three or more items, the comma ______ the last item from the first item in the series, not the first item from the last item. Taken together, these details imply a broader principle that extends beyond the immediate example, though the author stops short of claiming universal proof. Readers must weigh both the evidence presented and the limits the author acknowledges.',
  question_text = 'Which choice completes the text so that it conforms to the conventions of Standard English?',
